Interface DisplayItem

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BooleanVariableView, DiscreteNumericalVariableView, MultiSelectVariableView, NumericalVariableView, ProcedureVariableView, ReferenceItem, VariableView

    public interface DisplayItem
    Contains common properties for items to display to the user.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      VariableGroup getDisplayGroup()
      Returns the VariableGroup (for display) to which this DisplayItem belongs.
      java.lang.String getDisplayName()
      Returns the display name of this DisplayItem to show to the user.
      java.lang.String getFragmentName()
      Returns the jsp fragment that this DisplayItem will use to build inputs and display to the user.

      Returns the help text as an Optional.

      java.lang.String getReferenceInfo()
      Returns the reference/description information for this DisplayItem.
